s designed for the modern woman</p>\n  {% endif %}\n  <div class=\"tsukie-collection-divider\">\n    <span class=\"tsukie-divider-line\"></span>\n    <span class=\"tsukie-divider-icon\">✦</span>\n    <span class=\"tsukie-divider-line\"></span>\n  </div>\n</div>",
